--- Page 1 ---
 
SFP/SFP+ modules used with GAM 
GAM supports any generic MSA-compliant 1G/10G, here is a list of the most common models:

Brand: FS 
Model: SFP-GB-GE-T 
FS SFP-GB-GE-T 1000BASE-T RJ45 SFP Transceiver Module - FS.com

Brand: FS 
Model: SFP-10G-T  
Cisco SFP-10G-T-X Compatible 10GBASE-T SFP+ Copper RJ-45 30m Optical Transceiver Module

Generic 1000BASE-SX SFP Transceiver Module - FS.com
